&lt;h2 id="ca-signed-certificates"&gt;CA-Signed Certificates &lt;a href="#ca-signed-certificates" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;i class="material-icons align-middle"&gt;link&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="for-production-use"&gt;For Production Use &lt;a href="#for-production-use" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;i class="material-icons align-middle"&gt;link&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Production environments should use certificates signed by a trusted Certificate Authority.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Registering in Azure</title><link>https://entratool-docs.garrardkitchen.com/docs/certificates/registering/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://entratool-docs.garrardkitchen.com/docs/certificates/registering/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="registering-certificates-in-azure"&gt;Registering Certificates in Azure &lt;a href="#registering-certificates-in-azure" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;i class="material-icons align-middle"&gt;link&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn how to upload and manage certificates in Azure app registrations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id="prerequisites"&gt;Prerequisites &lt;a href="#prerequisites" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;i class="material-icons align-middle"&gt;link&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Before registering a certificate:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;✅ Certificate created (PFX format)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;✅ Azure app registration exists&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;✅ Appropriate permissions in Azure AD&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id="upload-certificate"&gt;Upload Certificate &lt;a href="#upload-certificate" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;i class="material-icons align-middle"&gt;link&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="via-azure-portal"&gt;Via Azure Portal &lt;a href="#via-azure-portal" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;i class="material-icons align-middle"&gt;link&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. Navigate to App Registration&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sign in to &lt;a href="https://portal.azure.com" rel="external" target="_blank"&gt;Azure Portal&lt;svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"&gt;&lt;path fill="currentColor" d="M14 5c-.552 0-1-.448-1-1s.448-1 1-1h6c.552 0 1 .448 1 1v6c0 .552-.448 1-1 1s-1-.448-1-1v-3.586l-7.293 7.293c-.391.39-1.024.39-1.414 0-.391-.391-.391-1.024 0-1.414l7.293-7.293h-3.586zm-9 2c-.552 0-1 .448-1 1v11c0 .552.448 1 1 1h11c.552 0 1-.448 1-1v-4.563c0-.552.448-1 1-1s1 .448 1 1v4.563c0 1.657-1.343 3-3 3h-11c-1.657 0-3-1.343-3-3v-11c0-1.657 1.343-3 3-3h4.563c.552 0 1 .448 1 1s-.448 1-1 1h-4.563z"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Navigate to &lt;strong&gt;Azure Active Directory&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Select &lt;strong&gt;App registrations&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Find and select your application&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
